# CRISPResso2 Architecture

CRISPResso2 is a software pipeline for analyzing genome editing outcomes from sequencing data.

## Core Components

- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoCORE.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoCORE.py): Main analysis engine
- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoShared.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoShared.py): Common utilities
- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoPlot.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoPlot.py): Visualization functions

## Analysis Modules

- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoBatchCORE.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoBatchCORE.py): Multiple experimental conditions
- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoPooledCORE.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoPooledCORE.py): Multiple amplicons from pooled experiments
- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoWGSCORE.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoWGSCORE.py): Whole genome sequencing sites
- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoCompareCORE.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoCompareCORE.py): Compare editing between samples
- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoAggregateCORE.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoAggregateCORE.py): Aggregate results

## Performance-Critical Components

- [CRISPResso2/CRISPResso2Align.pyx](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPResso2Align.pyx): Fast sequence alignment (Cython)
- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoCOREResources.pyx](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoCOREResources.pyx): Core computational resources (Cython)
- [CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoMultiProcessing.py](mdc:CRISPResso2/CRISPRessoMultiProcessing.py): Parallel processing

## Utility Scripts

- [scripts/filterReadsOnSequencePresence.py](mdc:scripts/filterReadsOnSequencePresence.py): Filter reads with specific sequences
- [scripts/countHighQualityBases.py](mdc:scripts/countHighQualityBases.py): Quality assessment

## Extensions

- [tools/chopchop/](mdc:tools/chopchop): CHOPCHOP integration for guide RNA design

## Entry Points

All modules have a `main()` function that serves as the entry point registered in [setup.py](mdc:setup.py).
